RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Woodway, WA operates under a mayor-council government. Mayor Mike Quinn's term is set to end on December 31, 2025. Council Member Rajeev Thakur's term for Position 1 also ends on December 31, 2025. Steve Gunn joined the Council in 2025 for Position 3, and Laura Murphy is transitioning to Council Member for Position 4. Councilmember Elizabeth Mitchell for Position 5 is retiring, and an appointment to fill this vacancy was scheduled for September 3, 2025. The General Election for Mayor, Council Position 1, 3, and 4 occurred on November 4, 2025, with results to be certified by November 26, 2025, and new terms beginning January 5, 2026.
